{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the cute world of Puzzle Crossing, a hybrid RPG Puzzle Adventure! Play Match-3 puzzles while casually helping your friends and townspeople. Collect and craft items, level up your abilities and use them to overcome new puzzle challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Explore</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with the overworld to meet new friends, find hidden items and discover new locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544680/extras/explore.png?t=1740500691\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Puzzle</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play fun match-3 puzzles and use your abilities and items to help you beat tougher challenges. With 12 upgradeable abilities and dozens of items you can choose your path to success!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544680/extras/puzzle2.png?t=1740500691\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Quest</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help solve the mystery of Springbank while also taking on other quests to help your friends and other NPCs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544680/extras/quest.png?t=1740500691\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3544680?t=1740500691","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3544680?t=1740500691","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544680/40eb563c96b91420c375f275dbf31ec3e42111f7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740500691","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstat